Package: countsplit
Title: Splitting a Poisson or negative binomial count matrix into independent training and testing matrices 
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Anna", "Neufeld", , "aneufeld@fredhutch.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the count splitting methodology from the paper "Inference after latent variable estimation for single cell RNA sequencing data" (Neufeld et al., 2022). 
